        <abstract>
            <p>Latitude overrules everything in distribution. Alpine distributions are like insular. Tabulating proportions.</p>
            <p>T. V. Wollaston’s Madeira insects: many flightless, thus not blown to sea. TVW’s insects do not confirm Forbes’s Atlantis.</p>
